rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0002
rows.name:
It's really been worth it coming all this
way to Acedia!

rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I've been studying the lifeforms in the
Cloud Sea around Acedia, and I've found
something interesting.

rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Currently, small creatures from other
countries...

rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0005
rows.name:
are growing to a size so large that
they might be classified as giant
species.

rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0007
rows.name:
This is the first time I've seen this
kind of thing too!

rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0008
rows.name:
I'd love to continue the study, but
my professor in Superbia is waiting
for my report...

rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0009
rows.name:
You'll take my report to Superbia
for me? That's great!

rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0010
rows.name:
You're very generous folk! I'm quite
touched by your kindness!

rows.label: tlk45300071_04_msg0011
rows.name:
Well, I really should crack on with
my study.
